        <item>
            <title>【评测】ROBOT 魂高达二号泰坦斯 A.N.I.M.E.　新设计关节超高可动</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/14/gundammkiianime/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=gundammkiianime</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/14/gundammkiianime/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Gary Lee]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 12:00:16 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[玩具]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1235703</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>ROBOT 魂的 ver. A.N.I.M.E. 今次启动了《机动战士 Z 高达》系列，第一阵作品就是黑色高达二号 GUNDAM Mk-II 泰坦斯。立即来看看表现如何。</p><p><a title="_DSC9325" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53720486706/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53720486706_3fcff539b2_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9325" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><h2>小美化工作大改善</h2><p>首先，小编一向玩 ROBOT 魂都会加点时间美化一下的，今次的高达 MKII 第一步就是上水贴，在坊间购买 HG 1:144 的高达 MKII Titans 水贴便可，水贴的 Size 都 Fit 好了的；上好所有水贴后下一步就是喷上一层消光处理，完成后就已经极靓仔了。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235711" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9253-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9253-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9253.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235712" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9259-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9259-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9259.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>开箱</h2><p>我们来看看这次本体高达 MK2 的外壳涂装及外型，主体高达高约 13cm，外型设计及比例上采用当年的动画风格设计，装上所有武装再摆出角木肇式立姿，甚有风范。整体的分色分件，以及涂装都细致，例如背后引擎位置内部也涂上了红色，制作上颇为用心。不过，外壳的蓝色及深蓝色则沿用了原始的塑胶颜色，这都是比较胶感的，要下点功夫美化一下才行 (简单喷层消光便可解决了)。</p><p><a title="_DSC9296" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53720699738/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53720699738_a2e135d9af_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9296" width="939" height="1024" /></a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235710" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9251-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9251-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9251.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><a title="_DSC9261" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53719585577/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53719585577_21bb7aa17d_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9261" width="591" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235714" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9270-353x580.jpg" alt="" width="353" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9270-353x580.jpg 353w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9270-scaled.jpg 548w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 353px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235713" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9267-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9267-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9267.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235715" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9271-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9271-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9271.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235717" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9265-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9265-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9265.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235718" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9266-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9266-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9266.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/22/bandai-g-frame/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Bandai 食玩乐园登陆葵芳     G-FRAME FA 风灵彩透 + MJ GUNDAM SP 版</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/22/gundam-breaker-4/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">《GUNDAM Breaker4》今年登场，特典版情报全公开</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2>新设计关节增加可动性</h2><p>现在让我们来测试一下这个模型的可动性。头部左右旋转没有问题，这次头部采用了拉出式关节，增加了可动范围。向前拉出时，嘴部可以碰到胸口；向后也可以抬起头部。手部可做 360 度旋转，手肘弯起超过 90 度。两肩的蝴蝶关节正常向前，还延伸了一个新设计，让手臂可以拉出，动作的幅度非常夸张，要摆出更有型的动作 Pose 时是非常实用的。腰部的左右旋转不错没有阻碍，向前弯腰约 30 度，亦可向后仰起，虽然幅度不大，但已经能够做到向上飞的动作，这个设计非常不错的。腰部左右也可以作轻微活动，高达 MK2 整体的关节松紧度也适中。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235719" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9273-601x580.jpg" alt="" width="601" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9273-601x580.jpg 601w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9273.jpg 932w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 601px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235720" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9275-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9275-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9275.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235721" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9276-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9276-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9276.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235722" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9277-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9277-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9277.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235723" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9278-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9278-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9278.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235724" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9279-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9279-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9279.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235725" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9280-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9280-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9280.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235726" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9282-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9282-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9282.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235727" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9286-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9286-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9286.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>丰富的配件</h2><p>武器及特效件应有尽有，武装包括伸缩盾牌、镭射枪、超级火箭炮和挂在头上的火神炮，镭射剑；而特效方面则有镭射直剑、镭射弯剑、喷射位特效，以及镭射枪光线特效。而最贴心的是，肩甲，膝甲，及后裙甲，均可替换上印有 1 号及 2 号的装甲零件。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235731" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9284-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9284-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc9284.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235728" src="h