        <item>
            <title>iOS 17.5 正式推出　Pride Radiance 动态桌布 + 维修不需关掉 Find My</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/14/ios-17-5/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ios-17-5</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/14/ios-17-5/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 11:00:28 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提电话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iOS 17.5]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1235617</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">Apple 正式推出 iOS 17.5。iOS 17.5 新功能多达 19 项，有全新 LGBTQ+ 社群文化、跨平台追踪蓝牙通知等功能。让小编介绍一下几项重要功能。</p><h2></h2><h2><strong>跨平台追踪侦测功能</strong></h2><p>Apple 将与 Google 推出跨平台追踪侦测功能，用家更新 iOS 17.5 后，可避免用家受到不明蓝牙追踪配件跟踪，只要发现相容蓝牙追踪器跟随使用者移动，跨平台追踪侦测将会通知用家。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1235620 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot20240514at-10-694x397.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="397" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot20240514at-10-694x397.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot20240514at-10.jpg 1184w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲用家更新 iOS 17.5 后，可避免用家受到不明蓝牙追踪配件跟踪</p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/14/ios-android/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">iOS 17.5 及 Android 追踪侦测警报，打击第三方蓝牙追踪装置</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/08/ios-17-5-rc/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">iOS 17.5 RC 版推出　维修时不用关闭 Find My 功能</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2>新增 Pride Radiance 动态桌布</h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">Apple 为支持 LGBTQ+ 社群文化，在 iOS 17.5 加入五张 Pride Radiance 新桌布，适用于 iPhone 和 iPad 或 Apple Watch。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1235618 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot20240514at-8-694x388.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot20240514at-8-694x388.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot20240514at-8.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ iOS 17.5 加入五张 Pride Radiance 新桌布</p><h2></h2><h2><strong>iPhone 维修不用再关掉 Find My</strong></h2><p>iOS 17.5 在寻找 Find My 加入「维修状态」新功能，用家在维修 iPhone 时，不需要关闭 Find My 功能，即可为 iPhone 进行维修。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1235619 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot20240514at-9-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot20240514at-9-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot20240514at-9.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲用家在维修 iPhone 时，不需要关闭 Find My 功能</p><h2>iPhone 输入耶路撒冷不再显示巴勒斯坦国旗</h2><p>现时更新至 iOS 17.5 后，用家输入耶路撒冷的英文，再不会出现巴勒斯坦国旗。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1235622 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot20240514at-11-694x386.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="386" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot20240514at-11-694x386.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot20240514at-11-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲用家输入耶路撒冷的英文，再不会出现巴勒斯坦国旗</p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/14/ios-android/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">iOS 17.5 及 Android 追踪侦测警报，打击第三方蓝牙追踪装置</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/08/ios-17-5-rc/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">iOS 17.5 RC 版推出　维修时不用关闭 Find My 功能</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2>eSIM 新功能</h2><p>为配合 M4 iPad Pro 和 M2 iPad Air 取消实体 SIM 卡， iOS 17.5 现时可能透过连结，直接启动 iPhone eSIM 服务。不再需要用相机扫描 QR Code 才可使用 eSIM。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1235623 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot20240514at-12-694x402.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="402" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot20240514at-12-694x402.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot20240514at-12.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲iOS 17.5 现时可能透过连结，直接启动 iPhone eSIM 服务</p><h2>Apple News + 文字游戏</h2><p>Apple News+ 将加入每日文字游戏，订阅了 Apple News 的用户可以用方块组成单字获取分数。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1235624 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot20240514at-13-694x389.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="389" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot20240514at-13-694x389.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot20240514at-13.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Apple News+ 将加入每日文字游戏</p><h2>Apple News 离线模式</h2><p>Apple News+ 新增离线模式，用户无论身在何处，或有没有连线上网，都可查阅 Apple News+上杂志、报纸等内容。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1235626 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot20240514at-14-694x459.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="459" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot20240514at-14-694x459.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot20240514at-14.jpg 1174w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Apple News+ 新增离线模式，没有连线上网，都可查阅 Apple News+</p><h2>书籍 App 设阅读目标</h2><p>为了让用家养成每日读书的好习惯，iOS 17.5 书籍 App 新增了阅读目标功能提醒。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1235629 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot20240514at-15-592x580.jpg" alt="" width="592" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot20240514at-15-592x580.jpg 592w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot20240514at-15.jpg 919w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 592px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲iOS 17.5 书籍 App 新增了阅读目标功能提醒</p><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2024/05/apples-2024-pride-collection-shines-light-on-lgbtq-plus-communities/">Apple</a>、<a href="https://www.techradar.com/how-to/how-to-use-find-my-iphone">Techradar</a>、<a href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/21/23969948/apple-airtag-bluetooth-tracker-black-friday-deal-sale">The Verge</a>、<a href="https://www.bbc.com/news/technology-68831685">BBC</a>、<a href="https://www.zdnet.com/article/iphone-15-esim-how-to-transfer-your-phone-number-to-apples-new-iphone/">ZDNET</a>、<a href="https://www.php.cn/faq/743810.html">PHP、</a><a href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/13/24155638/apple-news-plus-offline-ios-17-5-macos-apple-watch-updates">The Verge</a>、<a href="https://www.cnet.com/tech/services-and-software/ios-17-5-your-iphone-just-got-all-these-features/">Cnet</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/14/ios-android/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">iOS 17.5 及 Android 追踪侦测警报，打击第三方蓝牙追踪装置</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/08/ios-17-5-rc/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">iOS 17.5 RC 版推出　维修时不用关闭 Find My 功能</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/14/ios-17-5/mobile-phone/">iOS 17.5 正式推出　Pride Radiance 动态桌布 + 维修不需关掉 Find My</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
